ent": "天真的孩子在玩耍", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020684}, {"id": 218679, "content": "操着一口不标准的当地方言，和那些小商小贩们打哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068975}, {"id": 218680, "content": "当地有特色的民居，特殊食材是一种令人感到兴奋的体验。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1062264}, {"id": 218681, "content": "有特色的建筑 街道", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 286987}, {"id": 218682, "content": "大清早去当地的路边摊和当地人一起吃早点", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068992}, {"id": 218684, "content": "感觉最有特色的是风景", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068995}, {"id": 218940, "content": "如果是城市旅居，那么我会关注街上的广告和公共标识；如果是旅游参观景点或者体验民族文化，我会关注风俗习惯(也就是导游？？)。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1063127}, {"id": 218693, "content": "方言听不懂的地方，比如吴语系，粤语系。满满的地方特色！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1048616}, {"id": 218694, "content": "当地环境氛围", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058868}, {"id": 218695, "content": "美食，美景，美人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1046162}, {"id": 218703, "content": "菜市场！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669290}, {"id": 218704, "content": "可以跟爱人发现各个方面的好玩东西", "image": "img/option/option/20170703185036k7IN4BAVryaMH9bm.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1069032}, {"id": 218705, "content": "碰到实在人多聊几句。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054169}, {"id": 218706, "content": "别具一格的建筑和风俗人情。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1065864}, {"id": 218707, "content": "方言和老市区", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038425}, {"id": 218708, "content": "小吃街（小吃＋街）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1069041}, {"id": 218709, "content": "美女", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068951}, {"id": 224341, "content": "古建筑或博物馆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1085498}, {"id": 226390, "content": "当地人的素质", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1093659}, {"id": 218711, "content": "去别的城都去书店看看，圣彼得堡的书店、柬埔寨极少数的书店、国内的独立书店", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 910973}]}